Our Features

Responsive Layout

Modulus is fully responsive and can adapt to any screen size. Resize your browser window to view it!.

Awesome Slider

Modulus includes two types of slider. You can use both Flex and Elastic sliders anywhere in your site.

Font Awesome

Font Awesome icons are fully integrated into the theme. Use them anywhere in your site in 6 different sizes!

Typography

Modulus loves typography, you can choose from over 500+ Google Fonts and Standard Fonts to customize your site!

Retina Ready

Modulus is Retina Ready. So, Everything looks amazingly sharp and crisp on high resolution retina displays of all sizes!

Excellent Support

We truly care about our customers and theme's performance. We assure you that you will get the best after sale support like never before!

Webulous Themes

Modulus uses advanced Redux Framework for theme options panel, you can customize any part of your site quickly and easily!

Page Builder

Modulus supports Page Builder. All our shortcodes can be used as widgets too. You can drag and drop our widgets with page builder visual editor.

Page Layout

Modulus offers many different page layouts so you can quickly and easily create your pages with no hassle!

Custom Widget

We offer many custom widgets that are stylized and ready for use. Simply drag & drop into place to activate!

Shortcode Builder

Modulus includes lots of shortcodes, and our shortcode builder, users can easily build custom pages!

Demo Content

Modulus includes demo content files. You can quickly setup the site like our demo and get started easily!

With advanced theme options, page options & extensive docs, its never been easier to customize a theme!

Testimonials

With our testimonial post type, shortcode and widget, Displaying testimonials is a breeze.

Social Media

Want your users to stay in touch? No problem, Modulus has Social Media icons all throughout the theme!

Google Map

Modulus includes Goole Map as shortcode and widget. So, you can use it anywhere in your site!

Multiple Portfolio

7 portfolio layouts, 3 blog layouts and multiple other alternate layouts for interior pages!

Multiple Sidebar

Unlimited sidebars allow you to create custom sidebars that match the style and layout of pages!
